outputs.output_descr:
The programme is intended to deepen democratic governance and improve service delivery, through the development of fully operational democratic, accountable and responsive regional and woreda (district) government institutions. It support capacity development including institution and system of the regional and local governments through the integration of a set of focused initiatives, including:
1.Local government capacity development at bureau (regional) and woreda (district) levels;
2.Local development funding for basic infrastructure and services at woreda level (UNCDF);
3.Local Economic Development (LED) from both the public investment and inclusive financing perspectives;
4.Documentation of Lessons Learned and Best Practices
